    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"\"\npage-layout: full\ntoc: false\nanchor-sections: false\nexecute:\n  freeze: auto\nlisting:\n  id: blog-listing\n  contents: blog\n  type: default\n  sort: \"date desc\"\n  fields: [image, date, title, categories, reading-time]\n  image-height: 64px\n  filter-ui: false\n  categories: false\n---\n\n::: {.page-band}\n[08 — Blog]{.label}\n\n::: {.h1}\nWriting on methods, systems\n:::\n\nI built this space to keep my published work in one easy-to-link place — papers, talks, code, data.\n\nAlso, to force myself to write more often about the messy parts of research that don’t make it into papers.\nThe plan is to post short pieces — methods notes, dataset cleanups, dead-ends, and the occasional opinion — alongside the formal publications. If you’re reading this and want to talk, my email is on the About page.\n\n— Edgar\n\n<div class=\"filter-bar\" data-filter-group=\"true\" data-filter-target=\"#listing-blog-listing\">\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn is-active\" data-filter=\"All\">All</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Brazil\">Brazil</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Data\">Data</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Data Analysis\">Data Analysis</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Decent Work\">Decent Work</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Energy Transition\">Energy Transition</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Methods\">Methods</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Mexico\">Mexico</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Modern Slavery\">Modern Slavery</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"Public Health\">Public Health</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filter-btn\" data-filter=\"R\">R</button>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"filt